'''Nubia Star Drives, Incorporated''',<ref name="Unlimited Power">''[[Unlimited Power]]''</ref> shorted to '''Nubia Star Drives, Inc.''',<ref name="BMF 47">{{BuildFalconCite|47|Starship Fact File}}</ref> or referred to as '''Nubian Design Collective''', was a manufacturing company. It notably produced the [[J-type 327 Nubian royal starship|J-type 327 Nubian starship]], the [[T-14 hyperdrive generator]] and certain sublight engines. Although its unique spaceframe was built in the [[Naboo]]an [[city]] of [[Theed]], the [[Naboo Royal Starship|Royal Starship]] used by [[Monarch of Naboo|Queen]] [[Padmé Amidala|Amidala]] was technically a modified Nubian Design Collective starship.<ref name="Ultimate Star Wars" />

